{"tid":359781,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"瓦努阿圖。斐濟的火光水光  (一) 行程加遊記","createTime":"2017-08-14T18:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T18:29:21.000Z","uid":136946,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"866788da32eaebaeec80f2a726ea1b91fa68e47a","tid":359781,"uid":136946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T18:14:46.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">多圖多字，長文慎入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFacebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/giegietraveltheworld/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgiegietraveltheworld%2F&d=hUosOSyPqjZlN3YTKGMQTP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5825df1b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/giegietraveltheworld/</a><br />\nBlog:<br />\n<a href=\"https://talk.cosmopolitan.com.hk/giegietraveltheworld/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftalk.cosmopolitan.com.hk%2Fgiegietraveltheworld%2F&d=hUosOSyPqjZlN3YTKGMQTP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=71f0d4d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://talk.cosmopolitan.com.hk/giegietraveltheworld/</a><br />\n<br />\n懶人一個，時隔半年，終於才決心打blog分享。當初在構想蜜月之旅時，想過去非洲馬達加斯加，可惜二月是非洲的雨季，而且是橫風橫雨，洪水截路的雨季，所以打消了這個念頭。但我想蜜月來得特別一點，不想單單在一個美麗的海島游游水，曬曬太陽便是，於是想起了斐濟，繼而想起廣告「瓦努阿圖，我想住既地方」猜想瓦努阿圖可能在斐濟附近，搜尋了一下地圖，果然在附近，所以我便提議了來一場斐濟加亞努亞圖之旅！<br />\n<br />\n我想很多香港人對於瓦努阿圖的認識僅限於那一句廣告詞，如果有睇《世界零距離》可能又會知多一點點，但始終認知有限，開初也有點擔心，不知要否打疫苗，要否Visa等，加上2015年的風災影響嚴重，擔心到了仍是一片頹桓敗瓦。於是上Trip Advisor尋找意見，有當地人回覆已修復得很好，所以便姑且一信！不用打疫苗，特區護照或BNO不用簽證，終於訂機票酒店出發！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Day One - Day Two&nbsp;天晴&nbsp;溫度30C&nbsp;</span><br />\n<br />\n要去瓦努阿圖，要先飛斐濟再轉機，我們搭斐濟航空香港直飛到斐濟，十個鐘機程，還好，不太累。斐濟航空既Staff服務挺好，我吃完正餐後，過了一個鐘多以後，又餓了！走到空姐休息的地方就問問有沒有多的食物，我可以買，但她就直接多給我一個餐，終於吃飽，可以睡了。<br />\n<br />\n到了斐濟南迪Nadi機場，有Live Band歡迎<br />\n<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-AHJPqbC1oTY/WXWbG-FYdzI/AAAAAAAAqpk/-DFnAab6Un8HvU5WIf_1fXdm26sPGf-DgCLcBGAs/s640/20170129_030107.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-AHJPqbC1oTY%2FWXWbG-FYdzI%2FAAAAAAAAqpk%2F-DFnAab6Un8HvU5WIf_1fXdm26sPGf-DgCLcBGAs%2Fs640%2F20170129_030107.jpg&h=cc71231c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n早上七點多到了斐濟，下午二點多才轉飛到瓦努阿圖，有點時間，行理寄在機場，便坐的士到市中心逛逛，大概40元港幣，可以講點價，但都差不多了。<br />\n<br />\n市中心的印度廟Sri Siva Subramaniya Temple<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20287223_10212757274343468_3056148428122796289_o.jpg?oh=47408e65a4773ec0e77da325579797e8&amp;oe=59FCB234\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20287223_10212757274343468_3056148428122796289_o.jpg%3Foh%3D47408e65a4773ec0e77da325579797e8%26oe%3D59FCB234&h=cf725166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20247541_10212757274423470_2657276921829030269_o.jpg?oh=e4879ca76198fd4e90f1079f5b750d1e&amp;oe=59EB796F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20247541_10212757274423470_2657276921829030269_o.jpg%3Foh%3De4879ca76198fd4e90f1079f5b750d1e%26oe%3D59EB796F&h=e5d1e215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n斐濟意外地多印度人，司機，侍應，酒店員工都是印度人，當然公務員如入境處官員便是斐濟人，聽當地人說很多斐濟人聘請了不少印度人來打工，其後亦有不少印度人移民過來做生意，所以市中心便出現了一個印度廟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20369649_10212757284343718_830667244522491703_o.jpg?oh=0dc34a5a693f63d9b00ef380dc4ea39d&amp;oe=5A080B20\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20369649_10212757284343718_830667244522491703_o.jpg%3Foh%3D0dc34a5a693f63d9b00ef380dc4ea39d%26oe%3D5A080B20&h=d30ef079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n毛都無一條的市中心大街！<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20286761_10212757275903507_1443711252046909476_o.jpg?oh=a3d314440e82913ed036622a51f7a630&amp;oe=59F6A0FD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20286761_10212757275903507_1443711252046909476_o.jpg%3Foh%3Da3d314440e82913ed036622a51f7a630%26oe%3D59F6A0FD&h=b83e8c45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們到斐濟那天是星期天，什麼店也沒開，斐濟在工作時工作，休息時休息這點上，做得很徹底，於是便急忙google，發現附近有個遊輪碼頭可以購物吃飯，便去了吃個早餐。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20248259_10212757274503472_3741550340587248043_o.jpg?oh=4cd272ea76555b7f90b38cb74bd4716f&amp;oe=5A0ECDC8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20248259_10212757274503472_3741550340587248043_o.jpg%3Foh%3D4cd272ea76555b7f90b38cb74bd4716f%26oe%3D5A0ECDC8&h=5297ad11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n味道還算可以，只是我吃不慣沒有炸的法式多士，哈哈。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20280363_10212757274383469_7275524235920552955_o.jpg?oh=7fa83e73d15be6efd6fc8ce9c48ce9e9&amp;oe=5A0AB098\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20280363_10212757274383469_7275524235920552955_o.jpg%3Foh%3D7fa83e73d15be6efd6fc8ce9c48ce9e9%26oe%3D5A0AB098&h=fb776dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下午一點多，回到機場轉飛到瓦努阿圖了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20248158_10212757273583449_8039428845699189738_o.jpg?oh=eb064982802c52969da4f6f46e158f84&amp;oe=59EC6945\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20248158_10212757273583449_8039428845699189738_o.jpg%3Foh%3Deb064982802c52969da4f6f46e158f84%26oe%3D59EC6945&h=065fd85c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n是小型機，而且還是螺旋槳機，真心有少少淆底！<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20280363_10212757273543448_2328446149141732068_o.jpg?oh=d5ee14e4714ef4c6fb68ad91b57940ba&amp;oe=59F20FD7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20280363_10212757273543448_2328446149141732068_o.jpg%3Foh%3Dd5ee14e4714ef4c6fb68ad91b57940ba%26oe%3D59F20FD7&h=c644ad6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但南太平洋的景色真是令人嘆觀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20280255_10212757273503447_4042416647596361580_o.jpg?oh=b8b2248d93cd8cbc46e31eb472a8b704&amp;oe=59EB2985\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20280255_10212757273503447_4042416647596361580_o.jpg%3Foh%3Db8b2248d93cd8cbc46e31eb472a8b704%26oe%3D59EB2985&h=025d942c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20280350_10212757272503422_8482034099545129551_o.jpg?oh=25af7e4b05798ae241b3f086cac8e116&amp;oe=59F45AA3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20280350_10212757272503422_8482034099545129551_o.jpg%3Foh%3D25af7e4b05798ae241b3f086cac8e116%26oe%3D59F45AA3&h=0665ea8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20232840_10212757353385444_6504309686084749048_o.jpg?oh=4589294c683a651b0388b262be1e6190&amp;oe=59FA9C46\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20232840_10212757353385444_6504309686084749048_o.jpg%3Foh%3D4589294c683a651b0388b262be1e6190%26oe%3D59FA9C46&h=f5b45893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"581f22a74d4de9c5c03077a6f691e645941ae3ef","tid":359781,"uid":136946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T18:15:09.000Z","msg":"終於到了瓦努阿圖的Port Vila，基本上和斐濟一樣，瓦努阿圖由多個小島組成，我們去了Port Vila，因為我們明天要轉飛去Tanna Island看火山，這裡最近。不過我知道挺多人去Malakula島，因為那邊沙灘和resort都不錯，不少國內遊客都鐘意去這個島，反而Tanna Island外國遊客會較多，可能喜歡火山多點。其實來到斐濟和瓦努阿圖令我驚訝是國內和台灣遊客好多，但香港遊客幾乎是零，只有我們兩個，可能我們在非當地旺季來了吧。據司機說八九月才是旺季，因為非雨季，我的天！不去非洲就是為了避開雨季，結果。。。不過瓦努阿圖和想象中的差不多，很熱很熱，但是乾熱，微風吹來還挺舒服！<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20232776_10212757342465171_2166946676101224354_o.jpg?oh=b1c14190cb554d20bca607296ef27e88&amp;oe=59F43BF7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20232776_10212757342465171_2166946676101224354_o.jpg%3Foh%3Db1c14190cb554d20bca607296ef27e88%26oe%3D59F43BF7&h=99df4bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n很快從機場來到市中心的 Mango Resort，五分鐘車程<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20232341_10212757343425195_3581384225146891156_o.jpg?oh=078ed27dac1b851e0876f138cf4ed08c&amp;oe=5A097F0C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20232341_10212757343425195_3581384225146891156_o.jpg%3Foh%3D078ed27dac1b851e0876f138cf4ed08c%26oe%3D5A097F0C&h=a277d323&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20248106_10212757342505172_2588696661118787762_o.jpg?oh=3dbbf953f83a800f80cf1c5a0fbd6b7d&amp;oe=5A0553D7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20248106_10212757342505172_2588696661118787762_o.jpg%3Foh%3D3dbbf953f83a800f80cf1c5a0fbd6b7d%26oe%3D5A0553D7&h=b9a6b7ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMango Resort 對著湖景，好靚好靚！<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/20286974_10212757342545173_5091827706474256039_o.jpg?oh=a4eaa0c90d84e25dc5a67d0b8d098c79&amp;oe=59FDDD91\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F20286974_10212757342545173_5091827706474256039_o.jpg%3Foh%3Da4eaa0c90d84e25dc5a67d0b8d098c79%26oe%3D59FDDD91&h=7fccb31a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二天收皮，很快有第三天的更新！謝謝。"},{"pid":"e9a7ce3b5dfa35b3f229684b89e4d44c7ecc25db","tid":359781,"uid":33566,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T18:21:01.000Z","msg":"國內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咩國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed14c89c964d388a24699129ba499e8ace32c6bf","tid":359781,"uid":136946,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T18:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你咩國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人，LOL，唔使gum敏感啊？"}]}